{"tid":1666152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好不安丫 咁多監控燈柱","createTime":"2019-10-21T00:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T00:53:20.000Z","uid":187007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebeafcf1390dae31fc5faad74afbe597397b54b","tid":1666152,"uid":187007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/08/30/hkgovernment/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F08%2F30%2Fhkgovernment%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=4ee08016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/08/30/hkgovernment/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">先唔提點解政府口述同報告經常不一，個試驗計劃又無詳細資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n係民意反浪聲音咁大既時候 政府仲要起多幾枝新既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">怕唔怕會有示威者發起活動 全洗折柱嫁</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後又拎黎做路障 又放火咁好驚驚丫 <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔排除警察可以靠燈柱追查到示威者身份 <br />\n<br />\n但都要小心示威者會發起活動全港清柱 搵到香港又唔安寧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔鼓吹暴力行為，千祈唔好 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞全港清柱大行動丫<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n擔心安全既小市民上 （利伸唔會自殺）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}